        "jsCode": "const state = $input.first().json;\n\n// Define the flags exactly as the next node expects them\nconst hasLocation = !!state.location;\nconst hasType = !!state.property_type;\nconst hasPrice = !!state.max_price || !!state.min_price;\n\nconst readyToSearch = hasLocation && hasType;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    ...state,\n    readyToSearch,\n    hasLocation,\n    hasType,\n    hasPrice\n  }\n}];"
